            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9050,
            "LocalizeKR": "죄송합니다. 이런 생각,\n메이드로서는 실격일 텐데.",
            "LocalizeJP": "申し訳ございません…\nこんな考え、メイドとしては\n失格のはずなのに。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20019,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001901,
            "DisplayOrder": 370,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8550,
            "LocalizeKR": "저는 자신감을 잃고 있었어요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "私…自信を\nなくしておりました。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20019,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001901,
            "DisplayOrder": 380,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 15000,
            "LocalizeKR": "주인님은 늘\n많은 것을 짊어지시고,\n그러신데도 괜찮다며 웃으시고.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ご主人様はいつも多くのものを\n背負っていて、それなのに\n大丈夫だと笑っていて。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20019,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001901,
            "DisplayOrder": 390,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12000,
            "LocalizeKR": "저는… 전혀 그 짐을\n대신해서 들어드리지 못하고…",
            "LocalizeJP": "私は…全然その重荷を、\n代わりに持って\n差し上げられず…。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20019,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2001901,
            "DisplayOrder": 400,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11500,
            "LocalizeKR": "그렇지만 주인님의\n대답으로, 다시 자신감을\n찾을 수 있을 것 같아요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ですが、ご主人様の\nお言葉で、再び前を\n向けそうです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
